nt|The next scenario is titled "Partner has the A@d". In that scenario declarer can't discard his diamond losers without drawing trumps. And since we have control of the trump suit we have nothing to worry about. When partner takes his club ruff he will cash the A@d or we can play a diamond when we win with the trump K. What we do now is again irrelevant.|
